OL,3,C'It just feels right': Stars on Soccer
OL,4,CAid, the World Cup, and Manchester
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FFormer England players Jill Scott and
OL,8,FWayne Rooney spoke at a press event
OL,9,Fahead of the 20th anniversary of
OL,10,FSoccer Aid.
OL,12,FEngland legend Jill Scott has
OL,13,Fdescribed her experience playing
OL,14,Falongside Wayne Rooney in last year's
OL,15,FSoccer Aid as a true "pinch me" moment
OL,16,Fas they both prepare to return for the
OL,17,Fcharity match's 20th anniversary.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
