PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772885576
OL,3,C'It just feels right': Stars on Soccer
OL,4,CAid, the World Cup, and Manchester
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FAmong the new faces joining the lineup
OL,8,Fis I'm a Celebrity winner and Youtuber
OL,9,FAngry Ginge and Warrington's own Owen
OL,10,FCooper: the Adolescence star who is
OL,11,Fmaking history as the youngest player
OL,12,Fto ever grace the pitch.
OL,14,FThe award-winning actor, said that
OL,15,Feven though he was not born when the
OL,16,Ffirst Soccer Aid took place he is a
OL,17,F"big fan" of the fundraising event,
OL,18,Fand being the youngest player to take
OL,19,Fpart is a "real honour".
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@IO]{D@KOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
