OL,3,C'It just feels right': Stars on Soccer
OL,4,CAid, the World Cup, and Manchester
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FThe 16-year-old from Warrington will
OL,8,Fjoin athletes and celebrities to
OL,9,Ffundraise for UNICEF at the London
OL,10,FStadium in the Queen Elizabeth Olympic
OL,11,FPark on 31 May 2026.
OL,13,FWayne Rooney
OL,15,FThe former Manchester United forward
OL,16,Ffrom Croxteth in Liverpool got to roll
OL,17,Fback the years in the 2025 Soccer Aid
OL,18,Fmatch, in which he scored at the
OL,19,FStretford End.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772885576
OL,3,C'It just feels right': Stars on Soccer
OL,4,CAid, the World Cup, and Manchester
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FHe said: "I've always loved Soccer Aid
OL,8,Fand what it does. This year is it's
OL,9,F20th year and it's raised #120 million
OL,10,Fwhich is incredible.
OL,12,F"Obviously raising money is the most
OL,13,Fimportant thing, but you also get to
OL,14,Fmeet from different people from
OL,15,Fdifferent backgrounds."
OL,17,FRooney's appearance in the 2026
OL,18,FEngland squad will see him play his
OL,19,Fthird Soccer Aid match, and hopefully
OL,20,Fhand him his first win.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772885577
OL,3,C'It just feels right': Stars on Soccer
OL,4,CAid, the World Cup, and Manchester
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FHe said: "I've never won before, so
OL,8,Fhopefully I can turn that around this
OL,9,Fyear."
OL,11,FThe England squad lost 5-4 at Old
OL,12,FTrafford in 2025.
OL,14,FThe 40-year-old also said that he
OL,15,Fhopes his old club will be turning it
OL,16,Faround after a difficult season, with
OL,17,FHead Coach Michael Carrick in charge
OL,18,Fof Manchester United until at least
OL,19,Fthe end of the season.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772885577
OL,3,C'It just feels right': Stars on Soccer
OL,4,CAid, the World Cup, and Manchester
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FHe said: "Of course Manchester United
OL,8,Fwill be looking at different
OL,9,Foptions... but it just looks right and
OL,10,Ffeels right with Michael Carrick in
OL,11,Fthere.
OL,13,F"It feels like a Manchester United
OL,14,Fteam of old, and so if that continues
OL,15,Fthere will be massive pressure for him
OL,16,Fto stay on."
OL,18,FWayne Rooney is also optimistic about
OL,19,FEngland's chances in the 2026 World
OL,20,FCup with new Manager Thomas Tuchel in
OL,21,Fcharge.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772885577
OL,3,C'It just feels right': Stars on Soccer
OL,4,CAid, the World Cup, and Manchester
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FHe said: "We're one of the favourites
OL,8,Fto win it. We have to be with the
OL,9,Fplayer's England has got and now with
OL,10,Fthe manager who had won various top
OL,11,Ftrophies throughout his career.
OL,13,F"I think we're in as good of a
OL,14,Fposition as we can be going into the
OL,15,FWorld Cup."
OL,17,FPlaying alongside the Manchester
OL,18,FUnited legend Wayne Rooney will be
OL,19,Frival club Manchester City's own hero:
OL,20,Fmidfielder Jill Scott.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
