FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772885577
OL,3,C'It just feels right': Stars on Soccer
OL,4,CAid, the World Cup, and Manchester
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FThe 39-year-old from Sunderland was
OL,8,Fpart of the Lionesses squad that won
OL,9,Fthe Euros in 2022, and has more than
OL,10,F160 caps for her country.
OL,12,FDespite her accolades, Scott says
OL,13,Fplaying alongside Wayne Rooney and
OL,14,FMichael Carrick in the 2025 Soccer Aid
OL,15,Fwas a highlight.
OL,17,FShe said: "Passing the ball to Wayne
OL,18,FRooney, such a Man United and England
OL,19,Flegend, was such a pinch me moment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772885577
OL,3,C'It just feels right': Stars on Soccer
OL,4,CAid, the World Cup, and Manchester
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,F"I was playing midfield with Michael
OL,8,FCarrick and just thinking; Jill just
OL,9,Frun and work hard. To do that with ex-
OL,10,FMan United legends at Old Trafford...
OL,11,Fit was such a good day."
OL,13,FJill Scott was also just as optimistic
OL,14,Fas her 2025 teammate Wayne Rooney
OL,15,Fabout England's chances at the World
OL,16,FCup.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772885577
OL,3,C'It just feels right': Stars on Soccer
OL,4,CAid, the World Cup, and Manchester
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FShe said: "I'm so excited for the men,
OL,8,FI really am. You could make two teams
OL,9,Fof 11 and they could both compete so
OL,10,FI'm so excited for them. Hopefully
OL,11,Fthey can go out there and win the
OL,12,Fworld cup, imagine!"
OL,14,FFormer England and Manchester City
OL,15,Fgoalkeeper Joe Hart is pulling his
OL,16,Fgloves back on to raise money for
OL,17,FUNICEF.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772885577
OL,3,C'It just feels right': Stars on Soccer
OL,4,CAid, the World Cup, and Manchester
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,F"I loved it last season. It was a
OL,8,Fgreat opportunity and something I
OL,9,Flooked at when I was playing the game
OL,10,Fand thought it would be something I'd
OL,11,Flove to get involved in, and it was
OL,12,Feverything I wanted and more. Great
OL,13,Fpeople for a great cause, and a
OL,14,Fspecial evening.
OL,16,FThe game was brilliant, but I want to
OL,17,Fwin. I play to win and there's no
OL,18,Fgetting away from that," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772885577
OL,3,C'It just feels right': Stars on Soccer
OL,4,CAid, the World Cup, and Manchester
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FHe's optimistic about Manchester
OL,8,FCity's chances in the Premier League
OL,9,Ftoo: "Obviously I'm always going to
OL,10,Fhave my Manchester City hat on when it
OL,11,Fcomes to the Premier League.
OL,13,F"We all know if Manchester City click
OL,14,Finto gear they can put real pressure
OL,15,Fon whoever's above them.
OL,17,F"You're always looking to win, there's
OL,18,Fno getting away from it. Everyone in
OL,19,Fthat team, everyone in that stadium,
OL,20,Feveryone in that coaching staff is
OL,21,Fthere to win."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
