OL,3,C'It just feels right': Stars on Soccer
OL,4,CAid, the World Cup, and Manchester
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FTickets for Soccer aid are available
OL,8,Fnow, and the charity match will be
OL,9,Fbroadcast live on ITV1 on 31 May 2026.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
